		<RichText x="67" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#a3320c" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#a3320c">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="698" width="479" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">帝王头上的双角，<span color="#ffbfbf">64火</span><span>盾，免疫扩散带来的攻击，破坏后20s开始挖地，随后恢复双角；<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>破坏时，损失</span><span color="#ffbfbf">10%生命值</span><span>，12s后恢复双角。<br/></span><span color="#bfffbf">(N4) </span><span>熔火双角存在时</span><span color="#ffbfbf">+33%攻击力</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="826" width="508" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">帝王场地内不断刷新的特殊「坚盾重甲蟹」，数量维持在3只，其上的元素护甲拥有<span color="#ffbfbf">12火</span><span>盾，护罩破坏后失控撞向帝王，造成真实伤害并</span><span color="#ffdfbf">破坏等量的熔火双角</span><span>，随后自杀；真实伤害的值由存活期间的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">60%水伤+10%非水伤</span><span>构成，上限不超过帝王的15%生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
